snippet.title: Skyworld - PS VR Announcement Trailer [PEGI]
snippet.description: Skyworld is a VR strategy game that throws together classic turn-based strategy, deck building and fast-paced real-time battles, all reimagined for VR. Coming soon to PlayStation VR. http://skyworld-game.com
